metadata.name: Lian Faz #138
metadata.description:
Introducing Lian Faz, one of the 22 Budweiser Royalty artists. This Alternative R&BÂ musician is from Kazan, Russia and has 500 NFTs available, allowing early fans to proudly represent them.

This project and rewards are only obtainable by 21+ (or legal drinking age) NFT collectors. Terms and Conditions apply.
